://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster?fbclid=IwAR3ykjbM3UuzBhIHriL0CY_lSjAAngWSlwsd8H4mz07mLDN8oZNZyiVd8SA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3ykjbM3UuzBhIHriL0CY_lSjAAngWSlwsd8H4mz07mLDN8oZNZyiVd8SA&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=6ebae30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster?fbclid=IwAR3ykjbM3UuzBhIHriL0CY_lSjAAngWSlwsd8H4mz07mLDN8oZNZyiVd8SA</a><br />\n呢個petition 簽咗去。用盡一切方法廣傳。<br />\n呢個petition有兩點很重要：<br />\n1. 告知美國香港有相當一部份人已經認為香港已陷入人道災難，係非常嚴峻嘅境況<br />\n2. 請求美國物理層面介入香港今次嘅運動。即使佢哋唔嚟，佢地亦知道香港有相當一部份人唔介意佢地介入。為日後情況再惡化舖路。"},{"pid":"475ea0ebb13f86e0b578b8a5764b011c46754580","tid":1444263,"uid":40439,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4930b2e3bcb7cbdfd3efc5e1487f492411299fe","tid":1444263,"uid":186431,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"28bd26092aa9dc2fee7f70ced06375a542500692","tid":1444263,"uid":40439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"成場運動入面之中最型嘅光頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ZYuFiJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ZYuFiJ.jpg&h=c0e1ea9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2019/7/1563852695_v9-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2019%2F7%2F1563852695_v9-1280w.jpg&h=8d2694a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e49a1d833cd645b97f3b16ac64d35df178e83f5c","tid":1444263,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:00:47.000Z","msg":"睇到起雞皮...我係香港人！<br />\n<br />\n唔係仇警，大家一定要清楚知道點解要清算警隊。警暴（濫捕、濫告、不依法規）係暴政一部分，唔全面改革警隊、監警制度，只會令目前同將來爭取雙普選更加舉步維艱<br />\n<br />\n所以，絕對唔需要否認自己係針對警隊，針對警隊就係對準政權。唔通你淨係針對林鄭、唔針對政制，就會有雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷買<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與全港三罷<br />\n#各區集會<br />\n#出核彈麻包袋都唔割蓆<br />\n#直至政府跪低<br />\n#抵制一切紅媒相關商業活動"},{"pid":"b2b0b510fa52764354fd966e716748ecab846cfb","tid":1444263,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147878cb28d9d9378a4298404479b76bed6d225a","tid":1444263,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24012a4792d2f44462bee824234a1db6903ff5d","tid":1444263,"uid":257415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:02:06.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"48798efe1fcedc802bf44be82b74c4bf030a7b6f","tid":1444263,"uid":69473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"請幫忙聯署香港需要人道救援<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster&d=4z%2BvbskHrV%2FWTILUlLswqi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=b83f0cc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-medical-army-hong-kong-hong-kong-under-humanitarian-disaster</a><br />\n<br />\n只需填名和email，在email收信確認就可以<br />\n只用你1分鐘時間<br />\n幫幫香港，幫幫我們"},{"pid":"bedbb252a7d6619d62803bd324ddae18685a3ac0","tid":1444263,"uid":61343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:05:13.000Z","msg":"保安只係保護顧客同商戶 仲有商場內環境<br />\n冇幫示威者啊！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/fac